  "detailed_description": "Kitten has moved to the countryside. Initially he has only three plantations of different sizes. Each of them presents a level of difficulty, and the biggest plantation is the one with the most water pipes. These pipes must be set in the correct position, so that the irrigation system can start working.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.poster.avif?t=1645709504\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.webm?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.mp4?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The kitten can also choose what to plant. It should be aware that the yield of each crop can vary. So it is smart to choose to plant what has a higher selling price.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.poster.avif?t=1645709504\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.webm?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.mp4?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At the end of each crop, the planting generates money. Kitten will use this money to fulfill his dreams as a cat, and finally have a large farm at his disposal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/118bad522f163c3eb39b8da97da96a6b.poster.avif?t=1645709504\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/118bad522f163c3eb39b8da97da96a6b.webm?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/118bad522f163c3eb39b8da97da96a6b.mp4?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Kitten has moved to the countryside. Initially he has only three plantations of different sizes. Each of them presents a level of difficulty, and the biggest plantation is the one with the most water pipes. These pipes must be set in the correct position, so that the irrigation system can start working.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.poster.avif?t=1645709504\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.webm?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/c80b639bf7b86c149d0224d6642d284a.mp4?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The kitten can also choose what to plant. It should be aware that the yield of each crop can vary. So it is smart to choose to plant what has a higher selling price.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.poster.avif?t=1645709504\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.webm?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721270/extras/498d3f092eda76fc7876b5c0bbf85b65.mp4?t=1645709504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At the end of each crop, the planting generates money. Kitten will use this money to fulfill his dreams as a cat, and finally have a large farm at his disposal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"